room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape Room Vero Beach in Port St. Lucie
room_description:
Many dreadful things have happened to the occupants of apartment 836B over the years, since the original tenants passing. Some people think the apartment is haunted by her spiteful spirit not wanting others to live in the place she once called home.

Recently, your friend Mary moved into the apartment because of the affordably low rent. Now she has disappeared.
